snippet.title: HOGWARTS LEGACY New Gameplay Demo 14 Minutes 4K
snippet.description:
Hogwarts Legacy Gameplay Demo New (State of Play 2022) for PC, PS5, XBOX SERIES X/S in amazing 4K ULTRA HD quality and improved from 30 FPS to amazing smooth 60 FPS.

Release date: Holiday 2022

Hogwarts Legacy is an upcoming action RPG set in the late 19th century in the Wizarding World developed by Avalanche Software and published by Warner Bros. Interactive Entertainment (Portkey Games).
